node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by John   Yunis on September 16, 2021 tagging @juliananuladesign, @baxter.streeter1, and @villafeltrinelli. May be an image of lake and nature.

node.text:
It was a year ago today that we lost my perfect, wonderful nephew, Maxcy Streeter. At the beginning of last year, we had started to discuss a trip to Italy, which obviously never happened, so I’d be so grateful if we could take a moment to send him love and light and to picture him here, in the chair by Lake Garda at Villa Feltrinelli, which he would have loved. 
Let’s hope that his spirit is resting in a place like this, and please send love ad light to his amazing brother, my perfect nephew, Baxter, who survives him and loves him very very much. 
Thank you all, so much! 
And thank you so much to @juliananuladesign for the perfect photo 
@villafeltrinelli #villafeltrinelli #maxcystreeter
